	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
