<li>ChinesePod: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://chinesepod.com/lessons/%E6%8A%8A-humbug">Qing Wen - 把 Humbug</a> (free podcast content)</li>
<li>FluentU: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.fluentu.com/chinese/blog/2015/04/01/mandarin-chinese-ba/">The Definite Guide to the Chinese Ba Construction</a></li>
<li>Mandarin Online: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://xmmandarinonline.com/2010/10/grammar-the-ba3-sentence/">把字句</a></li>
<li>Just Learn Chinese (blog): <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://justlearnchinese.com/lesson-10-how-to-understand-and-use-pattern-%E2%80%9C-%E6%8A%8A-%E2%80%9D-in-chinese/">Lesson 10 How to understand and use Chinese sentence pattern “…把…”?</a></li></ul>
<div style="display:none;">
<dl><dd>HSK5</dd></dl>
</div>
